Class HornAxiomVisitorEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owlapi.util.HornAxiomVisitorEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OWLAnnotationAxiomVisitorEx<Boolean>, OWLAxiomVisitorEx<Boolean>

    public class HornAxiomVisitorEx
extends Object
implements OWLAxiomVisitorEx<Boolean>
    Returns true if the visited axioms are an ontology in Horn-SHIQ form.
